== HitCounter ==

A very simple hit counter with little javascript and rails.

It is currently hosted in heroku [http://counter.heroku.com/].

It is a google gadget and it will start showing the number of visits made to the page 

by placing the gadget [http://counter.heroku.com/count/show].
or

by simply placing the following html element in your page.
<script src="http://counter.heroku.com/javascripts/count.js" type="text/javascript"></script>	
<div>Hit Count: <span id = "count"></span><div>

